    {
        "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748525",
        "quote": "The suffragettes were women of action. Their motto was 'Deeds not Words,' and the film reflects that with a number of big set pieces, from the smashing of windows in central London to a riot at the Houses of Parliament.",
