    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748537",
        "quote": "I'm very interested in cinema that explores emotional journeys and where you can use everything at your disposal cinematically to locate you inside someone's head and their emotional landscape.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sarah Gavron",
            "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748537"
