    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748535",
        "quote": "I think the main thing for young women is to have confidence and not be afraid to challenge continuing inequalities, because that's the only way you'll get change.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sarah Gavron",
            "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748535"
