    {
        "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748550",
        "quote": "The suffragettes realized the power of getting arrested and going to prison and harassing politicians and making a nuisance of themselves. It got them a lot of attention. What they never did was set out to endanger human life except for sacrificing themselves.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Sarah Gavron",
            "url": "/quotes/sarah_gavron_748550"
        },
        "topics": [
